This is a salt configuration to mainly configure linux workstation
The profile is defined by a grain called type to be set in the /etc/salt/minion file like :
grains:
  type: work

Then top file in salt dir use that for configuration.
Pillar contains specifics about packages and other distro based parameters

2014/01/03 : reviewing global arch in pure dev stage
pillar : 
	- have a static definition file to define variables like data filesystem
	- Have definition of main packages (like firefox apache ..) that change amongst distro

